<br>
And now the fun starts ... as a result of Sony's malthusianist strategy concerning spelldrops/quests, the first PoP spells are appearing in the Bazaar for insane prices.<br>
<br>
On Antonius Bayle, SHield of the Arcane was to be sold for 12k by a trader yesterday. Now guess what will be the prices of more &quot;vital&quot; spells like the new pets.<br>
<br>
Sony changed his strategy bewteen Luclin (all in all, relatively easy to obtain spells, despite some exceptions like 60 pet heal) and PoP obviously.<br>
<br>
So, if we are lucky, we will have a full spell book .... just before EQ 2 will be launched...<br>
<br>
BAH<br>
