<br>
Spells that NEVER sit in the bazaar for long will stay relatively high.  When multiple copies of a spell are sitting in the bazaar and no one is buying them - the prices WILL come down.<br>
<br>
The fortunate few who got the chance to sell the spells while the price was high - will likely be the ones that buy the high-priced spells from ANOTHER vendor....<br>
<br>
